# ==================== TERMS ====================

### Create Term
POST {{baseUrl}}/terms
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "programId": "{{programId}}",
  "name": "Fall 2025",
  "startDate": "2025-09-01",
  "endDate": "2025-12-31",
  "isCurrent": true
}

### Get All Terms
GET {{baseUrl}}/terms
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get Terms by Program
GET {{baseUrl}}/terms?programId={{programId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get Current Term Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/terms?isCurrent=true
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get Term By ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/terms/{{termId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Update Term
PUT {{baseUrl}}/terms/{{termId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Fall 2025 Updated",
  "isCurrent": false
}

### Set Term as Current
PUT {{baseUrl}}/terms/{{termId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isCurrent": true
}